# Oracle APEX PDF.js Viewer

A lightweight PDF viewer for Oracle APEX that renders PDF documents directly inside an APEX page using **PDF.js** and **Amazon S3 pre-signed URLs**.

Unlike the browser's native PDF viewer, this implementation works consistently across desktop and mobile browsers while providing built-in page navigation and zoom controls.

