## Features

- 📄 Display PDFs inside Oracle APEX
- ☁️ Supports Amazon S3 pre-signed URLs
- 📱 Mobile friendly
- 📖 Single-page navigation (Previous / Next)
- 🔍 Zoom from 10% to 250%
- ⚡ High DPI (Retina) rendering
- 🎨 Universal Theme compatible
- 🚫 No plugins required

