# Amazon S3 CORS

Your bucket must allow requests from your APEX application.

Example:

```json
[
  {
    "AllowedHeaders": ["*"],
    "AllowedMethods": [
      "GET",
      "HEAD"
    ],
    "AllowedOrigins": [
      "https://your-apex-domain.com"
    ],
    "ExposeHeaders": []
  }
]
```

Replace:

```
https://your-apex-domain.com
```

with your APEX application URL.

