# Rendering

The viewer renders **one page at a time**.

Benefits include:

- Faster rendering
- Lower memory usage
- Better mobile performance
- Large PDF support
- Similar user experience to Adobe Reader

---

# Mobile Support

The viewer has been tested with:

- Desktop Chrome
- Desktop Edge
- Desktop Firefox
- Android Chrome
- iPhone Safari
- iPhone Chrome

Since rendering is performed by PDF.js instead of the browser's built-in PDF viewer, behavior is consistent across supported browsers.

